timelineItems.desc:
Rachel Bonnetta takes you beyond the white lines and the obvious on Off Topic. #OFwRB

In the first episode, we head to Philadelphia to hang out with World Cup veteran and Union star midfielder Maurice Edu. He showed us a few of his favorite places in Philly, like where he buys his sneakers and, of course, where he gets a Philly cheese steak.
